    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons who introduce television or radio programs, often act as masters of ceremonies, make commercial announcements, and read brief items such as news summaries and sports reviews.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000042061/Webster's Third New International Dictionary (1961)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Personas que presentan programas de televisión o radio, a menudo actúan como maestros de ceremonia, hacen anuncios comerciales, y leen artículos breves tales como resúmenes de noticias y reseñas de deportes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Personen die televisie- of radioprogramma's inleiden, vaak als ceremoniemeesters optreden, reclameboodschappen aankondigen en korte berichten zoals nieuwssamenvattingen en sportverslagen voorlezen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>介紹電視或廣播節目的人，經常擔任各類儀式的主持人，進行廣告播報，以及朗讀新聞總結與體育評析等簡短的播報。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
